new tab comes up whenever I select the home button in addition to resetting the current page to home

Reproducible: Always

Steps to Reproduce:
1. open a tab and go to a site (other than home)
2. click on the home tab and the current page goes to home BUT

Actual Results:  
3. a new tab is generated in addition to the current one.

Expected Results:  
clicking on the home button should not open an additional tab
comments.author: jsudano@metrohealth.org
